5.text: Jeewaka and Yasith are very good friends. One day they watched a very interesting TV programme on birds at Jeewaka's house.
5.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'><phoneme alphabet='ipa' ph='dʒiːwəkə'>Jeewaka</phoneme> and <phoneme alphabet='ipa' ph='jaːsit̪'>Yasith</phoneme> are very good friends. One day they watched a very interesting TV programme on birds at <phoneme alphabet='ipa' ph='dʒiːwəkə'>Jeewaka</phoneme>'s house.</prosody></speak>

6.text: Yasith: It was a very interesting programme, wasn't it?
6.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'><phoneme alphabet='ipa' ph='jaːsit̪'>Yasith</phoneme>: It was a very interesting programme, wasn't it?</prosody></speak>

7.text: Jeewaka: It was indeed. I learnt many new things about birds.
7.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'><phoneme alphabet='ipa' ph='dʒiːwəkə'>Jeewaka</phoneme>: It was indeed. I learnt many new things about birds.</prosody></speak>

8.text: Yasith: That's true. This was the first time I've heard the names of certain birds.
8.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'><phoneme alphabet='ipa' ph='jaːsit̪'>Yasith</phoneme>: That's true. This was the first time I've heard the names of certain birds.</prosody></speak>

9.text: Jeewaka: Do you remember the beautiful white bird with a crest? It was very beautiful, wasn't it?
9.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'><phoneme alphabet='ipa' ph='dʒiːwəkə'>Jeewaka</phoneme>: Do you remember the beautiful white bird with a crest? It was very beautiful, wasn't it?</prosody></speak>

10.text: Yasith: Yes, you mean the Kagu? It's sad that it can't fly. Jeewaka: Hmm. By the way, would you like to know more about birds?
10.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'><phoneme alphabet='ipa' ph='jaːsit̪'>Yasith</phoneme>: Yes, you mean the Kagu? It's sad that it can't fly. <phoneme alphabet='ipa' ph='dʒiːwəkə'>Jeewaka</phoneme>: Hmm. By the way, would you like to know more about birds?</prosody></speak>

11.text: Yasith: Of course! They're beautiful creatures. I wish I could be as free as a bird and fly high in the sky.
11.ssml: <speak><prosody rate='slow'><phoneme alphabet='ipa' ph='jaːsit̪'>Yasith</phoneme>: Of course! They're beautiful creatures. I wish I could be as free as a bird and fly high in the sky.</prosody></speak>
